"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Dogecoin is a kind of inflation crypto. Since it will inflate, people believe it’s less worth investing than bitcoin and ethereum. However, they may ignore one important truth that the total inflation amount per year of dogecoin is fixed thus the inflation rate of dogecoin will be decreased gradually to near zero as time passed.\\n\\nLet’s draw a picture and testify this theory:\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/MgcTzX5KdomvCj5yqdTvF.jpg?height=420&width=560)\\n\\nwe can see, in ten years there will be 40% more dogecoin than today. Ten years, dogecoin circulating supply increase 40% while the price of dogecoin could fluctuate by 100% in a month.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/rjRoM05N_sVtU4r2d71Ke.jpg?height=420&width=560)\\n\\nAnd if we look at how the inflation rate change everyday, we could surprisingly find out that the inflation rate keeps decreasing as the circulating supply keeps increasing. The impact of inflation on dogecoin’s price will be less likely to be an problem.\\n\\nCorresponding to this is that more and more Gen Z-ers are comming to crypto world, and dogecoin with on doubt will be one of their most popular crypto. So let’s look forward to dogecoin’s future.\\n\\nTo Da Moon\",\"timestamp\":1634388836,\"title\":\"Is inflation a problem to Dogecoin?\"},\"digest\":\"dX92NAeL0iH3YEBkgM8x3q3DTpjIShnsqtA05RkPgKE\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xf9dCd7C5Cb97157F6249eE7960e9914443d88F74\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"k-R5Ouk89i-i97jdB4HySLrQADip3wQDrx_cGOTU_2g\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"OiulkizIR3J7HkGo9yYCLghigEUcgKXlF9Uj4SlaxZY\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"6d7cWfTaji5hHY6dDzJUE-z23YR4pon7SoCyxhz45EzLR4a9huoctqZEmdtmtCAflh3Xn965MPU33-GBdJsQYg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x00daa378ee7f2b45196057dd4dc4aa873c42a8a1e4665df954594a30c6b2125a730fbf8cdfd438b79e834da669211dee630376f7e78845f6c93